headline: Citi Maintains Buy Rating on Targa Resources Corp. (TRGP)
summary: Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE:TRGP) is one of the 13 best oil and gas storage stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On February 24, Citi analyst Spiro Dounis increased the firm’s price target for Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE:TRGP) from $200 to $262, resulting in a double-digit upside potential of more than 13%.
